cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the problem of multi-modal sensor registration for vehicle perception, which is a common topic in the field of computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed method involves the use of deep neural networks, which is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, these five categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
